{"tid":227954,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯真心挽完了","createTime":"2017-05-03T14:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T09:02:36.000Z","uid":101464,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19a4ca7080f926e7341aaa5f758cad1794a93176","tid":227954,"uid":101464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"又犯官非，個人又無哂鬥心，同十年前活潑開朗踢足球既佢相差太大，<br />\n當年佢球場上變化萬千，笑住入波，而家留哂鬍鬚，死氣沉沉咁踢，<br />\n同佢夾開既隊友一個少一個，就算仲健在既都老去殘去，<br />\n國家隊佢又收左皮，一代球王玩完了！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相反，c朗哩幾年反而更上一層，個人惡得黎惡得起惡得有人信服，<br />\n睇佢不斷打破驚人既紀綠，幾乎前無古人，而且佢既身心仍然好當打，<br />\n人又成熟左，連國家隊都有杯贏咗，長期保持高水準狀態！"},{"pid":"d18a58dab260676f5773b485a8192483381757cf","tid":227954,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:16:02.000Z","msg":"又想燈牙"},{"pid":"222b5a933f63833af7c1ac43ec96de04b43c8266","tid":227954,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"你就玩完<br />\n挽你老母"},{"pid":"03513a04c16ac70c1e0068662431f20a706fe742","tid":227954,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:17:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ty-FPov610I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTy-FPov610I&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=fe16eede\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ty-FPov610I</a>"},{"pid":"4f1dd6a716ebfa4bb55f89a2d6557037bd3742dc","tid":227954,"uid":102404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"08c6cf7abee38391beb2da99a2c4f54cce5ee31a","tid":227954,"uid":78117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f506beb9b664104a56d026a202b7d9aa71f3facc","tid":227954,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"牙梅食得太多薯片，真係唔得掂"},{"pid":"ab326c79b8e8692bfc64f75b32551c2465cda2b4","tid":227954,"uid":68711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco